---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>

<!-- ARTISTAS -->
<section class="seccion-artistas">
  <h2 class="titulo-seccion">ARTISTAS INVITADOS</h2>

  <div class="contenido">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1470225620780-dba8ba36b745" alt="DJ">

    <div class="texto">
		<li>
			<ul>Martin Garrix – Mainstage / EDM, uno de los más grandes del mundo.</ul>
		</li>

		<li>
			<ul>David Guetta – Leyenda del EDM y colaboraciones pop masivas.</ul>
		</li>

		<li>
			<ul>Tiësto – Histórico y aún en los festivales más grandes.</ul>
		</li>

		<li>
			<ul>Calvin Harris – EDM y pop electrónico, hits internacionales.</ul>
		</li>

		<li>
			<ul>Armin van Buuren – Trance icónico, influyente por décadas.</ul>
		</li>

		<li>
			<ul>Swedish House Mafia – Trance icónico, influyente por décadas.</ul>
		</li>

		<li>
			<ul>Charlotte de Witte – Techno moderno, reina de festivales europeos. </ul>
		</li>

		<li>
			<ul>Skrillex – Bass / Dubstep, pionero y mega influyente en el género.</ul>
		</li>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!--EXPERIENCIAS -->
<section>
  <h2 class="titulo-seccion">EXPERIENCIAS</h2>

  <div class="contenido inverso">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1506157786151-b8491531f063?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Festival">

    <div class="texto">
      <p>Baila al ritmo de la música electrónica junto al mar, con DJs internacionales y un ambiente lleno de energía. Disfruta de la playa, luces, efectos visuales y momentos inolvidables junto a miles de asistentes que comparten tu pasión por la música.</p>
      <p>Sumérgete en una experiencia única bailando al ritmo de la música electrónica frente al mar, donde las olas se mezclan con los beats más electrizantes.</p> 
      <p>Déjate llevar por sets de DJs internacionales que harán vibrar cada rincón del escenario, mientras luces deslumbrantes, láseres y efectos visuales crean un espectáculo sensorial que despierta todos tus sentidos.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- NEON HERO SECTION -->
<main class="heroe-neon">
  <div class="estrellas"></div>
  
  <div class="contenedor">
    <!-- DJ Icon -->
    <div class="seccion-dj">
      <svg class="icono-dj" viewBox="0 0 500 550" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs>
          <filter id="glow" x="-50%" y="-50%" width="200%" height="200%">
            <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="3" result="coloredBlur"/>
            <feMerge>
              <feMergeNode in="coloredBlur"/>
              <feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/>
            </feMerge>
          </filter>
          <filter id="blur-glow">
            <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="4"/>
          </filter>
        </defs>
        
        <!-- Glow background effect -->
        <ellipse cx="250" cy="350" rx="200" ry="150" fill="#ff1493" opacity="0.1" filter="url(#blur-glow)"/>
        <ellipse cx="250" cy="350" rx="150" ry="100" fill="#00ffff" opacity="0.08" filter="url(#blur-glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Decks Base -->
        <path d="M 80 300 L 420 300 L 430 450 L 70 450 Z" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="4" filter="url(#glow)" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        <rect x="75" y="305" width="350" height="140" rx="8" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="3" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Left Turntable outer -->
        <circle cx="140" cy="375" r="55" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="4" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="140" cy="375" r="45" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="3" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="140" cy="375" r="35" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="2" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="140" cy="375" r="15" fill="#00ffff" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Right Turntable outer -->
        <circle cx="360" cy="375" r="55" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="4" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="360" cy="375" r="45" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="3" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="360" cy="375" r="35" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="2" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="360" cy="375" r="15" fill="#00ffff" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Center control panel -->
        <rect x="200" y="320" width="100" height="110" rx="8" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="2" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Control buttons left column -->
        <circle cx="215" cy="335" r="5" fill="#ff1493" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="215" cy="355" r="5" fill="#7fff00" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="215" cy="375" r="5" fill="#ff6600" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="215" cy="395" r="5" fill="#00ffff" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Control buttons right column -->
        <circle cx="285" cy="335" r="5" fill="#ff1493" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="285" cy="355" r="5" fill="#7fff00" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="285" cy="375" r="5" fill="#ff6600" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="285" cy="395" r="5" fill="#00ffff" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Center fader -->
        <rect x="245" y="335" width="10" height="60" rx="2" fill="#ff1493" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- DJ Body - Hoodie -->
        <ellipse cx="250" cy="180" rx="70" ry="85" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="3" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <path d="M 190 180 Q 180 220 190 250" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="3" filter="url(#glow)" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <path d="M 310 180 Q 320 220 310 250" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="3" filter="url(#glow)" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        
        <!-- Hood outline -->
        <path d="M 200 140 Q 250 100 300 140 Q 280 150 250 150 Q 220 150 200 140" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="2" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- DJ Head -->
        <circle cx="250" cy="90" r="40" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="4" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Left Headphone Cup -->
        <circle cx="160" cy="60" r="30" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="4" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="160" cy="60" r="20" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="2" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Right Headphone Cup -->
        <circle cx="340" cy="60" r="30" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="4" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="340" cy="60" r="20" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="2" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Headphone band left -->
        <path d="M 140 50 Q 120 20 160 20" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="3" filter="url(#glow)" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        
        <!-- Headphone band right -->
        <path d="M 360 20 Q 380 20 360 50" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="3" filter="url(#glow)" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        
        <!-- Headphone band top -->
        <path d="M 160 25 Q 250 -10 340 25" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="3" filter="url(#glow)" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        
        <!-- Visor/Glasses left -->
        <rect x="215" y="75" width="22" height="25" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="2" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <line x1="237" y1="87" x2="263" y2="87" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="2" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Visor/Glasses right -->
        <rect x="263" y="75" width="22" height="25" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="2" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Eyes glow -->
        <circle cx="220" cy="82" r="3" fill="#00ffff" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        <circle cx="268" cy="82" r="3" fill="#00ffff" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Left arm/hand -->
        <path d="M 185 210 Q 130 280 120 350" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="4" filter="url(#glow)" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <circle cx="120" cy="355" r="18" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="3" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Right arm/hand -->
        <path d="M 315 210 Q 370 280 380 350" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="4" filter="url(#glow)" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <circle cx="380" cy="355" r="18" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="3" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- Body center line -->
        <line x1="250" y1="180" x2="250" y2="270" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="2" filter="url(#glow)"/>
        
        <!-- DJ's label "DJ's" -->
        <text x="250" y="490" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="48" font-weight="bold" text-anchor="middle" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="2" filter="url(#glow)">DJ's</text>
        
        <!-- Music bars on right -->
        <g filter="url(#glow)">
          <rect x="420" y="240" width="12" height="50" fill="none" stroke="#ff1493" stroke-width="2"/>
          <rect x="420" y="210" width="12" height="80" fill="none" stroke="#00ffff" stroke-width="2"/>
          <rect x="440" y="220" width="12" height="70" fill="none" stroke="#7fff00" stroke-width="2"/>
          <rect x="460" y="200" width="12" height="90" fill="none" stroke="#ff6600" stroke-width="2"/>
        </g>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Title -->
    <div class="titulo-principal">
      <h1 class="linea-titulo-1">siente el</h1>
      <h1 class="linea-titulo-2">heat</h1>
      <h1 class="linea-titulo-3">se parte de</h1>
      <h1 class="linea-titulo-4">la música</h1>
    </div>

    <!-- Party Text -->
    <div class="seccion-fiesta">
      <p class="fiesta-rosa">PARTY!!</p>
      <p class="fiesta-rosa">PARTY!!</p>
      <p class="fiesta-verde">PARTY!!</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Experience Text -->
    <div class="texto-experiencia">
      <p>Vive la experiencia<br>que marcará el<br>último año <br>de tu vida!!</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Love You Text -->
    <div class="texto-amor">
      <p>love<br>you<br>baby</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pleasure Text -->
    <div class="texto-placer">
      <p>El placer<br>que<br>vibra</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Cartel -->
    <div class="texto-cartel">
      <p>CARTEL</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <img src="camion.webp" alt="camion">
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@700&family=Poppins:wght@400;700&display=swap');

  .heroe-neon {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: #000000;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .estrellas {
    position: absolute;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-image: 
      radial-gradient(2px 2px at 20% 30%, #eee, rgba(0,0,0,0)),
      radial-gradient(2px 2px at 60% 70%, #fff, rgba(0,0,0,0)),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 50% 50%, #ddd, rgba(0,0,0,0)),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 80% 10%, #fff, rgba(0,0,0,0)),
      radial-gradient(2px 2px at 90% 60%, #eee, rgba(0,0,0,0)),
      radial-gradient(1px 1px at 30% 80%, #ddd, rgba(0,0,0,0));
    background-size: 200% 200%;
    animation: twinkle 5s ease-in-out infinite;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  @keyframes twinkle {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.5; }
    50% { opacity: 1; }
  }

  .heroe-neon .contenedor {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100vh;
    perspective: 1000px;
  }

  /* DJ Section */
  .seccion-dj {
    position: absolute;
    top: 10%;
    left: 5%;
    width: 150px;
    height: 150px;
  }

  .icono-dj {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
  }

  .tornamesa-dj {
    position: absolute;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 30%, #ff00ff, #ff00ff);
    border-radius: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    box-shadow: 
      0 0 20px #ff00ff,
      0 0 40px #ff00ff,
      0 0 60px #ff00ff,
      inset -2px -2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    border: 2px solid #ff00ff;
  }

  .tornamesa-dj::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #00ffff, #00ffff);
    border-radius: 50%;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px #00ffff;
  }

  .auriculares-dj-izquierda,
  .auriculares-dj-derecha {
    position: absolute;
    width: 30px;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00ffff, #ff00ff);
    border-radius: 50% 50% 20% 20%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px #00ffff, inset 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    top: 5px;
  }

  .auriculares-dj-izquierda {
    left: -10px;
    transform: rotateZ(-45deg);
  }

  .auriculares-dj-derecha {
    right: -10px;
    transform: rotateZ(45deg);
  }

  /* Main Title */
  .titulo-principal {
    position: absolute;
    top: 15%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    text-align: center;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .titulo-principal h1 {
    margin: 5px 0;
    font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }

  .linea-titulo-1 {
    color: #fff;
    text-shadow: 
      0 0 10px #00ffff,
      0 0 20px #00ffff,
      0 0 30px #00ffff;
  }

  .linea-titulo-2 {
    color: #fff;
    text-shadow: 
      0 0 10px #00ffff,
      0 0 20px #00ffff,
      0 0 30px #00ffff,
      0 0 40px #00ffff;
    font-size: 4rem;
  }

  .linea-titulo-3 {
    color: #fff;
    text-shadow: 
      0 0 10px #00ffff,
      0 0 20px #00ffff,
      0 0 30px #00ffff;
  }

  .linea-titulo-4 {
    color: #fff;
    text-shadow: 
      0 0 10px #00ffff,
      0 0 20px #00ffff,
      0 0 30px #00ffff,
      0 0 40px #00ffff;
  }

  /* Party Section */
  .seccion-fiesta {
    position: absolute;
    right: 3%;
    top: 12%;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .fiesta-rosa,
  .fiesta-verde {
    margin: 8px 0;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .fiesta-rosa {
    color: #ff1493;
    text-shadow: 
      0 0 1px #ff1493,
      0 0 2px #ff1493,
      0 0 40px #ff1493,
      0 0 50px #ff1493;
  }

  .fiesta-verde {
    color: #7fff00;
    text-shadow: 
      0 0 1px #7fff00,
      0 0 2px #7fff00,
      0 0 40px #7fff00,
      0 0 50px #7fff00;
  }

  /* Experience Text */
  .texto-experiencia {
    position: absolute;
    left: 2%;
    top: 40%;
    color: #0088ff;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
    font-style: italic;
    text-shadow: 
      0 0 10px #0088ff,
      0 0 20px #0088ff,
      0 0 30px #0088ff;
    max-width: 250px;
  }

  /* Love You Text */
  .texto-amor {
    position: absolute;
    right: 25%;
    top: 45%;
    color: #00ff00;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-shadow: 
      0 0 10px #00ff00,
      0 0 20px #00ff00,
      0 0 30px #00ff00;
  }

  /* Pleasure Text */
  .texto-placer {
    position: absolute;
    right: 2%;
    top: 65%;
    color: #ff6600;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-shadow: 
      0 0 10px #ff6600,
      0 0 20px #ff6600,
      0 0 30px #ff6600;
  }

  /* Cartel Text */
  .texto-cartel {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 8%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    color: #e0529e;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-shadow: 
      0 0 10px #ff1493,
      0 0 20px #ff1493,
      0 0 30px #ff1493,
      0 0 40px #ff1493,
      0 0 50px #ff1493;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .titulo-principal h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .linea-titulo-2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .fiesta-rosa,
    .fiesta-verde {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .linea-titulo-1,
    .linea-titulo-2,
    .linea-titulo-3,
    .linea-titulo-4 {
      text-shadow: 
        0 0 5px,
        0 0 10px,
        0 0 15px;
    }

    .texto-cartel {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }

</style>

<style>

*{
  margin:0;
  padding:0;
  box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
  background:#000;
  color:#fff;
  font-family:'Poppins', sans-serif;
}

section{
  padding:100px 12%;
}

.titulo-seccion{
  font-family:'Orbitron', sans-serif;
  font-size:48px;
  font-weight:800;
  letter-spacing:3px;
  margin-bottom:60px;
